式开始前一天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tv-on-the-radios-blistering-staring-at-the-sun-performance-on-fallon-3815110">在<em>吉米·法伦 (Jimmy Fallon)</em>亮相之后</a>——乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tv-on-the-radio-surprise-intimate-show-new-yorks-tv-eye-reunion-tour-3815730">在可容纳 250 人的纽约场馆 TV Eye 演出了一场惊喜演出</a>。</p><p> TV On The Radio 计划今天（11 月 30 日）结束他们在韦伯斯特音乐厅为期四天的纽约驻场演出，然后于 12 月前往洛杉矶和伦敦。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Ftv-on-the-radio-tickets%2Fartist%2F904793" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买洛杉矶演出的门票， <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DTV%2520on%2520the%2520radio" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买英国演出的门票。</p><p>明年夏天，他们还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796">在巴塞罗那的 Primavera Sound 演出</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/khruangbin-announce-biggest-headline-show-gunnersbury-park-tv-on-the-radio-buy-tickets-3800167">在伦敦 Gunnersbury 公园的大型户外演出中为 Khruangbin 提供支持</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tv-on-the-radio-perform-wolf-like-me-and-more-for-npr-tiny-desk-debut-3817307">Watch TV On The Radio 表演“Wolf Like Me”以及 NPR“Tiny Desk”首秀的更多内容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
